import React from 'react'
import Banner from '../../compponents/banner/Banner'

import Menu from '../../compponents/menu/Menu'
import Footer from '../footer/Footer'

  return (
    <>
    <Banner/>
    <Cooking/>
    <Menu/>
    <Footer/>
    <FoodCard/>
    </>
  )
}

export default Home
